Jungle Grass is tall grass found all over Ape Atoll, Crash Island, Mos Le'Harmless and Mudskipper Point. Staying in the jungle grass on Ape Atoll makes Monkey Archers unaggressive to the player even if they do not have a Greegree equipped or have completed the Monkey Madness II quest.
